'''Annie Magdalen Matthews Tolkien''' ([[4 January]] [[1905]] — [[1970]]) was the wife of [[Hilary Tolkien]]. They were wedded in 1928 in Evesham, Worcestershire, England. They had three children - Gabriel, Julian and Paul. She was the sister-in-law of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]].

